Responsive website using HTML and CSS

--> Understanding Units 

- px

- % 



- vw,vh = screan ke sath width hight change krne keliye  font ka size change krna acording to divise 


- vmax,vmin = screan ke acroding font size lene keliye max ke hisanb se change krta hain
  

- em,rem = parent ke acording  size change krne keliye em
 rem 1rem = 16px



